      "solution": "According to the question and given conditions, possibilities of unloading are as follows. Mon Tue Wed Thur Fri K/L N/K J L/N M As per condition (iv) M is the second ship to be unloaded after J. Hence, if M is unloaded on Friday, then J will automatically be unloaded on the day falling two days before Friday i.e., Friday – 2 = Wednesday."
